value.0: Second Lieutenant Hedresh is one of Outpost Hope's medical officers. He tends to be on duty, and works tirelessly to keep the soldiers of the Republic alive. A fairly popular man, he's known to be a bit of a womanizer and has a reputation for appreciating good food.
